Topic: Simplification (VERY HIGH WEIGHTAGE 🔥)
1️⃣ Clear Theory (Easy Language)

Simplification means solving expressions quickly using:

BODMAS rule
Fractions
Squares & roots
Percent conversions

👉 In Railway exams, this is fast + scoring topic

2️⃣ Important Rules (BODMAS)

Order of solving:

👉 B → O → D → M → A → S

Brackets
Orders (powers, roots)
Division
Multiplication
Addition
Subtraction
3️⃣ Important Tricks
🔹 Squares (Learn)
11² = 121
15² = 225
25² = 625
30² = 900
🔹 Fractions to % (Fast)
1/2 = 50%
1/4 = 25%
1/5 = 20%
1/10 = 10%
🔹 Approximation Trick
49 ≈ 50
101 ≈ 100

👉 Used in fast calculation

🧠 Quick Tips
Always follow BODMAS
Solve bracket first
Avoid long calculation → use tricks
